      "body": "## Pull request overview\n\nThis PR introduces the Unit 6 “two-tier trust” system for `aienvs`, adding a per-project manifest pin (`trusted_sha`) plus per-user JSONL stores (`trust.jsonl` history + `pending.jsonl` queue), along with the initial `aienvs trust` cobra subcommand tree and a frozen spec document.\n\n**Changes:**\n- Add `internal/trust/` (types, decision engine, JSONL store + compaction, pending queue, minimal prompting) with unit tests and stable exit-code tests.\n- Add `internal/cli/cmd_trust.go` implementing the `aienvs trust` subcommands (status/pending/diff/promote/pin/verify/reset/add/revoke/allow-new-shas/compact) with CLI tests.\n- Add spec + plan doc updates, and new dependencies (`spf13/cobra`, `gofrs/flock`).\n\n### Reviewed changes\n\nCopilot reviewed 15 out of 16 changed files in this pull request and generated 11 comments.\n\n<details>\n<summary>Show a summary per file</summary>\n\n| File | Description |\r\n| ---- | ----------- |\r\n| internal/trust/types.go | Trust domain types, sentinel errors, validation helpers, exit-code constants |\r\n| internal/trust/types_test.go | Unit tests for kinds, SHA validation, entry validation, sentinel errors, exit codes |\r\n| internal/trust/store.go | Append-only trust.jsonl store, fold + compaction implementation |\r\n| internal/trust/store_test.go | Store fold/append/compact/concurrency tests |\r\n| internal/trust/pending.go | pending.jsonl queue: append, list/latest, clear via rewrite |\r\n| internal/trust/pending_test.go | Pending queue tests (idempotency, latest-per-URL, clear) |\r\n| internal/trust/policy.go | Pure decision engine (`Decide`), exit-code mapping |\r\n| internal/trust/policy_test.go | Decision engine table-style tests |\r\n| internal/trust/prompt.go | Minimal stdin prompts + revoked banner (no TUI dependency) |\r\n| internal/trust/prompt_test.go | Prompt flow tests and NO_COLOR behavior |\r\n| internal/cli/cmd_trust.go | Cobra `aienvs trust` command tree + manifest pin/verify wiring |\r\n| internal/cli/cmd_trust_test.go | CLI-level tests for trust subcommands and manifest writing |\r\n| docs/spec/trust-store-v1.md | Frozen v1 spec for trust.jsonl / pending.jsonl / manifest invariants |\r\n| docs/plans/2026-04-21-001-feat-aienvs-workspace-cli-plan.md | Marks Units 1–6 complete |\r\n| go.mod / go.sum | Adds cobra + flock dependencies |\n</details>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n---\n\n💡 <a href=\"/JustinBeaudry/aienvs/new/main?filename=.github/instructions/*.instructions.md\" class=\"Link--inTextBlock\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Add Copilot custom instructions</a> for smarter, more guided reviews. <a href=\"https://docs.github.com/en/copilot/customizing-copilot/adding-repository-custom-instructions-for-github-copilot\" class=\"Link--inTextBlock\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Learn how to get started</a>.",
      "state": "COMMENTED",
